---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Subtle Somatics — Gentle Transformation Within & Beyond" description="Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics with Kaja Possert-Bienzle. Come home to the wisdom of your body. Vienna, Austria.">

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO — full-screen atmospheric + personal intro
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <p class="hero-hi anim-fade">Hi, I'm Kaja.</p>
          <h1 class="anim-fade anim-d1">Come home to the<br/>wisdom of your body.</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub anim-fade anim-d2">Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics for those ready to meet themselves at the depth where transformation naturally unfolds.</p>
          <div class="hero-btns anim-fade anim-d3">
            <a href="#connect" class="btn btn-glow">Book a free discovery call</a>
            <a href="#philosophy" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-portrait anim-fade anim-d2">
          <div class="portrait-ring"></div>
          <img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-scroll">
        <span>Scroll</span>
        <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       INVITATION — dark poetic section
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="invitation">
    <div class="invitation-inner">
      <div class="inv-decoration">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" class="inv-circle"><circle cx="60" cy="60" r="55" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.15"/><circle cx="60" cy="60" r="35" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.1"/></svg>
      </div>
      <p class="inv-pre reveal">I'm inviting you&hellip;</p>
      <div class="inv-lines">
        <p class="reveal"><em>to align</em> <span>with the free-flowing rhythm of your essence</span></p>
        <p class="reveal"><em>to unfold</em> <span>the luminous wonder of deeper aliveness</span></p>
        <p class="reveal"><em>to embody</em> <span>the radiant expression of your unique creativity, love and power</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="inv-divider reveal"><span></span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       PHILOSOPHY — warm, centred
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="philosophy" id="philosophy">
    <div class="philosophy-inner text-center">
      <p class="section-label reveal">Subtle Somatics</p>
      <h2 class="reveal">What if everything we need<br/>is already here?</h2>
      <p class="philosophy-body reveal">Subtle Somatics is not technique — it is cartography for the landscapes beneath language. Here, the body is not analysed, but deeply and attentively listened to — each sensation a doorway, each holding a request for recognition.</p>
      <p class="philosophy-body reveal">Within each person lies a vast reservoir of innate resources — strength, courage, compassion, trust, and peace. Not something to be acquired from outside, but something to be uncovered, remembered, and embodied from within.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       ABOUT — personal story with image
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-img reveal">
        <img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" />
        <div class="about-img-accent"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="section-label reveal">About Me</p>
        <h2 class="reveal">Unfolding companion.<br/>Wholeness witnesser.<br/>Integration facilitator.</h2>
        <p class="reveal">I believe that within every person lies a vast treasure of innate resources — strength, love, radiance, trust and peace. These qualities are not something to be acquired from outside, but something to be discovered, remembered and embodied from within.</p>
        <p class="reveal">What I deeply value about myself is my sincere, deep caring and my finely-tuned attunement that accompanies nourishment, healing and unfolding. I see and mirror qualities of resourcefulness in others — and I feel deeply honoured and blessed to offer Spinal Energetics and presence-based coaching.</p>
        <p class="reveal">My approach draws from the wisdom of the body-mind-soul system and works with the natural intelligence that already knows how to heal, integrate and align. Through gentle presence and deep listening, we create the conditions for what is most alive and true in you to come forward.</p>
        <div class="about-tags reveal">
          <span class="tag">Presence</span>
          <span class="tag">Wholeness</span>
          <span class="tag">Embodiment</span>
          <span class="tag">Trust</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       ARCHETYPES — dark section
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="archetypes">
    <div class="archetypes-inner">
      <div class="archetype reveal">
        <h3>The Space-Opener</h3>
        <p>Kaja does not direct, but accompanies. She widens a space that already exists — a space where people remember their own capacity to heal themselves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-divider"></div>
      <div class="archetype reveal">
        <h3>The Gardener & the Gondolier</h3>
        <p>She nurtures what wants to grow and unfold, with patience, mindfulness and trust in the natural process. At the same time, she navigates her clients through profound inner landscapes — not as one who steers, but as a gentle companion on a journey that happens by itself.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       PILLARS — encounter / unfolding / integration
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pillars-section" id="offerings">
    <div class="pillars-inner">
      <p class="section-label text-center reveal" style="color:var(--gold)">What I Offer</p>
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="color:var(--text-on-dark); margin-bottom:4rem;">Three movements toward wholeness</h2>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar reveal">
          <div class="pillar-accent">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" width="60" height="60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="25"/><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-num">I</span>
          <h3>An encounter</h3>
          <p>Truly getting to know the thoughts, emotions and sensations you have moment to moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-line"></div>
        <div class="pillar reveal">
          <div class="pillar-accent">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" width="60" height="60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"><path d="M30 5 C22 15, 18 22, 18 32 C18 42, 24 55, 30 55 C36 55, 42 42, 42 32 C42 22, 38 15, 30 5Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-num">II</span>
          <h3>An unfolding</h3>
          <p>Experiencing your vast inner resourcefulness — in the form of strength, love, presence and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-line"></div>
        <div class="pillar reveal">
          <div class="pillar-accent">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 60 60" width="60" height="60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"><path d="M10 30 Q20 12, 30 30 Q40 48, 50 30"/><path d="M10 30 Q20 48, 30 30 Q40 12, 50 30"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-num">III</span>
          <h3>An integration</h3>
          <p>Connecting into deeper coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       SERVICES — warm, detailed cards
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="services-inner">
      <p class="section-label text-center reveal">Services</p>
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:1rem">Two pathways, one intention</h2>
      <p class="text-center reveal" style="margin:0 auto 3.5rem; color:var(--text-soft)">Both honour the intelligence already present in you.</p>

      <!-- Subtle Coaching -->
      <div class="service-card-full reveal">
        <div class="scf-img">
          <img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" />
          <div class="scf-img-overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scf-body">
          <span class="scf-badge">Coaching</span>
          <h3>Subtle Coaching</h3>
          <p class="scf-lead">The art of initiating deep inner processes through subtle, almost invisible impulses.</p>
          <p>Informed by <strong>Aletheia Coaching</strong>, this approach invites you into deep presence — a place where insights and direction arise from your inner truth, not external pressure. Through deepening self-contact and gentle inquiry, qualities like courage, tenderness, clarity, and inner strength emerge — not as something new, but as something that was always there.</p>
          <p class="scf-note"><em>This is not talk therapy. It's an experiential exploration of what is present right now.</em></p>
          <ul class="scf-list">
            <li>Deepened access to innate qualities of strength, love, and presence</li>
            <li>Gently untangling inner polarities beneath habitual patterns</li>
            <li>Coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="scf-meta">
            <span>~60 min</span>
            <span>€130</span>
            <span>Online or in person</span>
          </div>
          <a href="#connect" class="btn">Book a session</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Spinal Energetics -->
      <div class="service-card-full reverse reveal">
        <div class="scf-img">
          <img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" />
          <div class="scf-img-overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scf-body">
          <span class="scf-badge se-badge">Energetics</span>
          <h3>Spinal Energetics</h3>
          <p class="scf-lead">Everything in us moves in spirals, in waves, in gentle fluctuations that know their own rhythm.</p>
          <p>At your core, you are strength, love, radiance and trust — and so many more qualities of resourcefulness. Imagine a treasure chest full of gems — each gem another nuance of resourcefulness that you can increasingly embody. It is already there. And often it is concealed by tension patterns of various kinds — emotional, physical, mental and spiritual.</p>
          <p>I invite you into a safe and courageous space so that these tension patterns may move and shift — and more and more of who you truly are can unfold.</p>
          <ul class="scf-list">
            <li>Deep surrender — your nervous system settling into safety</li>
            <li>Spontaneous movement as energy shifts and reorganises</li>
            <li>Emotional release — making space for clarity and connection</li>
            <li>Expansion — feeling more alive, more connected, more yourself</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="scf-meta">
            <span>~60 min</span>
            <span>€130</span>
            <span>In person · Vienna</span>
          </div>
          <a href="#connect" class="btn">Book a session</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       POETIC BREAK
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="poetic-break">
    <div class="poetic-inner text-center reveal">
      <blockquote>
        <p>To practice subtle somatics is to return to the body not as vessel, but as a field — alive, aware, and already knowing.</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       JOURNEY — what to expect
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="journey">
    <div class="journey-inner">
      <p class="section-label text-center reveal">Your Journey</p>
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem">What to expect</h2>
      <p class="text-center reveal" style="margin:0 auto 3.5rem; color:var(--text-soft); font-style:italic">Each step unfolds at its own pace — no rushing, no forcing.</p>
      <div class="journey-steps">
        <div class="j-step reveal">
          <div class="j-num-wrap">
            <span class="j-num">1</span>
            <div class="j-connector"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <h3>Discovery call</h3>
            <p>A free conversation to sense into whether this work resonates. I'll listen to what's alive for you, and together we'll feel into the right next step.</p>
            <span class="j-meta">~20 min &middot; Free &middot; Online</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="j-step reveal">
          <div class="j-num-wrap">
            <span class="j-num">2</span>
            <div class="j-connector"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <h3>Your session</h3>
            <p>Each session meets you exactly where you are. Whether coaching, spinal energetics, or both — the body leads, and I follow.</p>
            <span class="j-meta">~60 min &middot; €130 &middot; Online or in person</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="j-step reveal">
          <div class="j-num-wrap">
            <span class="j-num">3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="j-content">
            <h3>Integration</h3>
            <p>Deeper transformation unfolds over time. Allow yourself space after each session. A series of sessions supports sustained embodiment of your wholeness.</p>
            <span class="j-meta">Series of 5 &middot; At your own pace</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       IMAGE BREAK with quote
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="img-break">
    <img src="/images/kaja-secondary.png" alt="Kaja — presence and embodiment" />
    <div class="img-break-top"></div>
    <div class="img-break-bottom"></div>
    <div class="img-break-text reveal">
      <p><em>"Container schaffen, in denen die nächsten Generationen gut begleitet werden können."</em></p>
      <p class="img-break-translation">Creating containers in which the next generations can be well accompanied.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       VALUES — dark section
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="values">
    <div class="values-inner">
      <p class="section-label text-center reveal" style="color:var(--gold)">What Guides Me</p>
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="color:var(--text-on-dark); margin-bottom:3.5rem">Core values</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="val-card reveal">
          <div class="val-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20"/><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Presence</h3>
          <p>Being fully here — with what is. Not fixing, not striving, but meeting the moment with open awareness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card reveal">
          <div class="val-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20"/><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="13"/><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Wholeness</h3>
          <p>Recognising that you are already whole. Our work is about removing the layers that obscure this truth.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card reveal">
          <div class="val-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><path d="M24 4 C18 14, 14 22, 14 30 C14 38, 18 44, 24 44 C30 44, 34 38, 34 30 C34 22, 30 14, 24 4Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Embodiment</h3>
          <p>Living from the body's wisdom, not just the mind's understanding. True knowing happens in the tissues, the breath, the bones.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="val-card reveal">
          <div class="val-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" width="48" height="48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"><path d="M6 24 Q16 8, 24 24 Q32 40, 42 24"/><path d="M6 24 Q16 40, 24 24 Q32 8, 42 24"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Trust</h3>
          <p>Trusting the rhythm of your own unfolding. There is an intelligence at work in you that knows the way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       BACKGROUND — warm section
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="background">
    <div class="background-inner">
      <p class="section-label text-center reveal">Background</p>
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="margin-bottom:3rem">Training & Experience</h2>
      <div class="bg-grid">
        <div class="bg-card reveal">
          <h4>Education & Anthropology</h4>
          <p>Bachelor of Education + Bachelor of Arts in Anthropology</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card reveal">
          <h4>Teaching & Facilitation</h4>
          <p>Youth education, team building, mindfulness and leadership trainings</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card reveal">
          <h4>Relational Practice</h4>
          <p>Facilitating We-Spaces and Authentic Relating since 2022</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card reveal">
          <h4>Yoga & Energy Work</h4>
          <p>200h Yoga Teacher Training in India, Reiki Level I + II</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card reveal">
          <h4>Professional Highlights</h4>
          <p>Women's leadership trainings for the UN, retreat facilitation, somatic imaginal inner journeys</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card reveal">
          <h4>Coaching & Psychotherapy</h4>
          <p>Advanced Coaching Training (Aletheia), ongoing MSc in Integrative Psychotherapy</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center reveal" style="margin:3rem auto 0; color:var(--text-soft); max-width:600px; font-style:italic">Through these diverse pathways, my devotion remains the same: to accompany others into their innate wholeness and resourcefulness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       FAQ — dark section
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="faq-inner">
      <p class="section-label text-center reveal" style="color:var(--gold)">Questions</p>
      <h2 class="text-center reveal" style="color:var(--text-on-dark); margin-bottom:3rem">Frequently asked</h2>
      <div class="faq-container">
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>What happens in a Spinal Energetics session?</summary>
          <p>You remain fully clothed, lying on a massage table. Through gentle touch and intuitive presence, your body responds naturally — sometimes with subtle shifts, sometimes with dynamic movements. Sessions typically begin with arriving in stillness together.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>What is subtle coaching for?</summary>
          <p>For life transitions, cultivating presence, aligning with what matters most, and embodying resourcefulness. It is less about striving and more about allowing your truth to emerge.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>How is this different from therapy?</summary>
          <p>Therapy often focuses on resolving past wounds. Subtle Coaching is present- and future-oriented, supporting clarity, aliveness, and integration while respecting your wholeness.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>How many sessions do I need?</summary>
          <p>Every body responds uniquely. Some feel deep change after one session; others find that a series supports deeper integration. Often 3–6 sessions offer a strong foundation.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>Who is this for?</summary>
          <p>People in transition, those seeking clarity, or those longing to live attuned to life's flow. It's for anyone ready to meet themselves more deeply and move from that place. Also supportive for healers, creatives, and seekers of wholeness.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>Is Spinal Energetics safe?</summary>
          <p>Yes. The process honours your body's wisdom. Nothing is forced; your body sets the pace. Sessions may not be suitable for acute physical injuries, recent surgeries, or unmanaged mental health crises. Please share your medical history beforehand.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>What about integration after a session?</summary>
          <p>Integration continues after the session as your body reorganises. You may feel more spacious, tired, or energised. Gentle self-care, rest, journaling, time in nature, and hydration support this natural process.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       POETIC CLOSE
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="poetic-break poetic-warm">
    <div class="poetic-inner text-center reveal">
      <blockquote>
        <p>This is the work of becoming intimate with nuance: reading the breath behind the breath, the movement beneath stillness, the sound inside silence.</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       CONNECT — contact with working form
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="connect" id="connect">
    <div class="connect-inner">
      <div class="connect-left reveal">
        <p class="section-label">Connect</p>
        <h2>I'd love to have you.</h2>
        <p class="connect-body">I feel honoured to serve you — just where you are. Whether you're curious, ready, or somewhere in between — reach out.</p>
        <p class="connect-body">All that's required is openness and willingness to receive.</p>

        <div class="connect-details">
          <div class="connect-detail">
            <div class="cd-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="cd-label">Email</span>
              <a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="connect-detail">
            <div class="cd-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="cd-label">Instagram</span>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/subtlesomatics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@subtlesomatics</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="connect-detail">
            <div class="cd-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="cd-label">Location</span>
              <p>Online (Zoom) & in person — Vienna, Austria</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="connect-right reveal">
        <form class="connect-form" action="https://formsubmit.co/connect@subtlesomatics.space" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New message from subtlesomatics.space" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://subtlesomatics.space/draft-3" />
          <input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none" />
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="d3-name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="d3-name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="d3-email">Email <span class="req">*</span></label>
            <input type="email" id="d3-email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="d3-interest">I'm interested in</label>
            <select id="d3-interest" name="interest">
              <option value="">Choose one (optional)</option>
              <option value="discovery">Free Discovery Call</option>
              <option value="coaching">Subtle Coaching</option>
              <option value="spinal">Spinal Energetics</option>
              <option value="both">Both / Not sure yet</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
